SUMMARY:Wacky Plants of the World
DESCRIPTION:There are lots of amazing plants on our planet.  Join ecoEXPLORE Central as we dive into the wackiest plants\, including some right here at home in North Carolina! \nThis virtual program is especially for kids in grades K-8\, but everyone is welcome.  You do not need to join ecoEXPLORE before the program\, but should you choose to create an account for your child so they can get started documenting wildlife for scientists and earning prizes\, visit ecoexplore.net. \nRegister here
URL:https://naturalsciences.org/calendar/event/wacky-plants/
LOCATION:Virtual\, NC\, United States
CATEGORIES:Children,Citizen Science,K-12 Students,Virtual
ORGANIZER;CN="ecoEXPLORE%20Team":MAILTO:ecoexplore@naturalsciences.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:NC Museum of Natural Sciences
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260401T193000
